snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: Skyward Sword (Wii) E3 2010 Trailer
snippet.description: Nintendo Life - NINTENDO finally show us the first trailer for the upcoming Wii epic, due for release in 2011. More information at http://nintendolife.com
